Susan Hampshire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Hampshire 0 Susan Hampshire, Lady Kulukundis (born 12 May 1937) is an English actress, known for her many television and film roles. A three-time Emmy Award winner, she won for The Forsyte Saga in 1970, The First Churchills in 1971, and for Vanity Fair in 1973. Her other television credits include The Pallisers (1974), The Grand (1997–98), and Monarch of the Glen (2000–05).
